name: Iconscout - Icons, Illustrations & 3D Assets
description:
Seamlessly access millions of design assets within Figma


  • Search through and implement 4.3 million+ curated design assets with a single plugin
  • These include SVGs, vector icons, illustrations, and 3D graphics
  • More than 30,000 new assets are added every week
  • Enjoy instant access to all of your favorite creators’ assets
  • Check out Iconscout’s other plugins, all created with ❤️ to make designing simpler for everyone!
